# SEO OTTER Feature Summary

**Database and Models**
- SQLite DB helper to create engine, auto-create tables, and open sessions (`seootter/sqlite_db.py`).
- SQLModel entities for Website, GSCAnalytics, and IndexStatus with validation and unique constraints (`seootter/models.py`).
- Article table and CRUD utilities for SEO content tracking (`seootter/article.py`).

**Content Mapping and Parsing**
- Map sitemap URLs to local files across `.qmd`, `.md`, `.ipynb` (`seootter/content_mapper.py`).
- Parse frontmatter for metadata and notebooks, strip frontmatter, and extract headers (`seootter/content_parser.py`).
- Title/description length checks and content length threshold check (`seootter/content_parser.py`).
- Link extraction, internal/external classification, and image alt extraction (`seootter/content_parser.py`).
- Text utilities: normalize, phone detection, similarity ratio, and file helpers (`seootter/content_parser.py`).
- Arabic to slug conversion and file-to-slug mapping helpers (`seootter/content_parser.py`).

**SEO Analysis**
- Keyword density, keyword placement, and keyword-in-metadata checks (`seootter/seo_analysis.py`).
- H1 count validation with Quarto title handling (`seootter/seo_analysis.py`).
- Header distribution analysis (`seootter/seo_analysis.py`).
- Duplicate content detection and content grouping by similarity (`seootter/seo_analysis.py`).
- Keyword cannibalization analysis across articles (`seootter/seo_analysis.py`).

**SEO Report**
- Sync sitemap-mapped articles into DB and generate page-level SEO reports (`seootter/seo_report.py`).
- Per-page checks for title/description length, content length, H1, missing image alts, and link counts (`seootter/seo_report.py`).
- Site-wide duplicate title/description detection with similarity threshold (`seootter/seo_report.py`).

**Google Search Console (GSC)**
- OAuth flow, token handling, and verified sites listing (`seootter/gsc_client.py`).
- Date range helpers with 3-day delay handling (`seootter/gsc_client.py`).
- Fetch Search Analytics data from GSC (`seootter/gsc_client.py`).
- Store GSC data with upsert and query analytics by query, page, country, device, and date range (`seootter/gsc_storage.py`).
- Trends and aggregation helpers, plus batch import across dates (`seootter/gsc_storage.py`).

**Index Tracking**
- URL Inspection API integration to track index status (`seootter/index_tracking.py`).
- Store and query index status; list not-indexed pages (`seootter/index_tracking.py`).
- Fetch sitemap URLs and bulk index checks (`seootter/index_tracking.py`).

**Semantic Search**
- Qdrant-backed keyword vector store with SentenceTransformers embedding (`seootter/semantic_search.py`).
- Store, search, and filter keywords with performance metadata (`seootter/semantic_search.py`).
- Track keyword presence in content and manual importance flags (`seootter/semantic_search.py`).
